# Basic Selectors


### Tag Selector

```sass
h1 {
    background-color: red;
}
```
### ID Selector

```sass
#fancy {
    background-color: red;
}
```


### Descendant  Selector
:::tip note
This Selector selects child and grandchildren elements.
::: 
```sass
h1 #fancy {
    background-color: red;
}
```

### Class Selector

```sass
.small {
    background-color: red;
}
```


### Combinator Selector

```sass
h1.red {
    background-color: red;
}
```

### Unrelated Selector

```sass
h1.red, h3 #fancy {
    background-color: red;
}
```

### Universal Selector

```sass
/* Select all the tags*/
* {
    background-color: red;
}

/* Select all the tags inside class*/

.biggie * {
    background-color: red;
}
```
# Sibling and Child Selectors

### First Sibling Selector

```sass
/* Select the fist Paragraphs next to Header 1*/
h1 + p {
    color: red;
}
```


### General Sibling Selector

```sass
/* Select ALL Paragraphs next to Header 1*/
h1 ~ p {
    color: red;
}
```



